			<CASNumber>000554-13-2</CASNumber>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="en">Lithium carbonate is an inorganic compound, the lithium salt of carbonic acid. This white salt is widely used in processing metal oxides and is on the World Health Organization's List of Essential Medicines for its efficacy in the treatment of mood disorders such as bipolar disorder. It is an antimanic medication used to treat acute mania in bipolar disorder and as a mood stabilizer. It also helps to prevent or lessen the intensity of manic episodes.</common:generalComment>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="zh">碳酸锂是一种无机化合物，是碳酸的锂盐。这种白色的盐被广泛用于加工金属氧化物，并因其在治疗双相情感障碍等情绪障碍方面的疗效而被列入世界卫生组织的《基本药物清单》。它是一种抗躁狂症药物，用于治疗双相情感障碍的急性躁狂症，并可作为一种情绪稳定剂。它还有助于预防或减轻躁狂发作的强度。</common:generalComment>
